== Japanese ==
{{ja-kanjitab-top}}
! [[立]] || [[食]]
{{ja-kanjitab-bottom}}
===Etymology===
立ち from [[立つ]] ''to [[stand]]'' + 食い from [[食う]] ''to [[eat]]''


=== Noun ===
'''立ち食い''' ([[たちぐい]], [[tachigui]])

# Standing and eating; a standing collation.
# Eating at a street stall.


=== Verb ===
'''立ち食い'''する ([[たちぐい]]する, [[tachigui]] suru)

# To eat while standing.
# To eat at a street stall.
====Conjugation====
{{ja-suru|立ち食い|たちぐい|tachigui}}


